General.Name: Banxa Holdings Inc
General.Description: Banxa Holdings Inc. operates as a payments service provider for the cryptocurrency exchanges in Australia, North America, and Europe. The company provides Web3 on-and-off ramp solutions that allows end users to purchase cryptocurrency and NFT's using fiat currency. Banxa Holdings Inc. was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Melbourne, Australia.
